<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 24 at 12:18PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Localized Dense Freezing Fog Lingers...
Localized areas of dense freezing fog continue to linger about
the Gallatin Valley early this afternoon. If you encounter dense
fog, be prepared for slick conditions on roads and sidewalks due
to a potential thin layer of ice, and ensure that your headlights
are on.</description>
